    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> I don't think we need a special value for me it's pretty clear that if you remove it there will be no limit\n\nJust to be clear, there is always a limit (<1000 hits) and the maxPages should then be computed from the `answer.nbPages`.\n",
